            <button class="faq-toggle" aria-expanded="false">
              <span class="faq-icon"></span>
              Is L-mount a problem for lens selection?
            </button>
          </h3>
          <div class="faq-answer" style="max-height: 0; overflow: hidden;">
            <p>Not anymore. Sigma, Leica, and Panasonic all make L-mount lenses. You have access to affordable Sigma Art lenses and high-end Leica glass. Third-party options from TTArtisan and Viltrox expand choices further. L-mount is smaller than Sony E or Canon RF, but growing steadily.</p>
