            <button class="faq-toggle" aria-expanded="false">
              <span class="faq-icon"></span>
              Should I get the S5 II or S5 IIX?
            </button>
          </h3>
          <div class="faq-answer" style="max-height: 0; overflow: hidden;">
            <p>The IIX is identical hardware with unlocked video features: ProRes RAW, waveforms, and USB-C RAW output. If you're a serious video creator, the IIX is worth the extra $500. For hybrid shooters or photo-focused users, the standard S5 II is plenty.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
